text: Low Deep T or TJ Cases is a South-African singer, songwriter, and producer based in London. He is best known for his hit "Casablanca" produced in 2012, which ranked #1 for many weeks in "Bulgaria Top 20" in March–April 2013 as well as among "Europe Official Top 100" in August 2013.http://top40-charts.com/song.php?sid=35292 ==Discography== ===Albums=== *2019 Stronger Together *2012 We Are One *2011 Big Love ===Singles=== *2014: Got 2 Find Love *2012: Casablanca *2009: Fragile *2008: Nothing Better than Your Loving *1998: You Bring Me Joy *1997: Do It Again ==External links== *Official website ==References== Category:South African musicians Category:House musicians
